{"tid":648313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]尖東怪人","createTime":"2018-04-30T14:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T16:06:32.000Z","uid":99392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6a0914291bc8a357a2e12001a8787b6b024fb476","tid":648313,"uid":99392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"早幾個月前經過尖東 <br />\n見到有個怪人企係路中心 <br />\n郁都唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知今日行過拍緊拖冇留意<br />\n一抬起頭見到佢企撚咗係度<br />\n近到見到佢啲頭髮勁長指甲勁長<br />\n真係好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最撚恐怖係佢企係到郁都唔郁<br />\n長期望住個地下<br />\n仲有時個頭會不尋常咁係度扭動<br />\n屌有冇人見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/223136_6f872d9cd54887d64f56cde48f8bc8ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F223136_6f872d9cd54887d64f56cde48f8bc8ca.png&h=ebb3b24c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/223341_67452ff10afa7616b71b32527cd655a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F223341_67452ff10afa7616b71b32527cd655a3.png&h=d084f7b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30ad982872b7fb541548bcab0ca3f5c3c4729862","tid":648313,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfa813ed85cb68e6430ce11b79dc629047971d64","tid":648313,"uid":99392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30ad982872b7fb541548bcab0ca3f5c3c4729862","tid":648313,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"唔好嚇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed9341eb52f01